TESTING STRATEGY FOR PRODUCTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

UNIT TESTS (Target: 80%+ coverage)
-----------------------------------
Priority Components:
1. Utility functions (lib/utils.ts)
   - cn() - class name merging
   - formatCurrency()
   - formatDate()
   - debounce()
   - isMobile()

2. Custom Hooks
   - useCarousel (all functionality)
   - useHover (hover state management)

3. UI Components
   - Button (all variants and states)
   - Input (validation, error states)
   - Card (rendering, props)
   - Loading (all variants)

INTEGRATION TESTS
-----------------
Critical User Flows:
1. Product browsing and filtering
2. Store locator search and selection
3. Navigation and routing
4. Language switching
5. Mobile menu interaction

E2E TESTS (Optional but Recommended)
-------------------------------------
Tools: Playwright or Cypress
Critical Paths:
1. Complete product discovery flow
2. Service locator usage
3. Form submissions
4. Cross-browser compatibility

PERFORMANCE TESTS
-----------------
- Lighthouse scores (target: 90+)
- Core Web Vitals monitoring
- Bundle size analysis
- Image optimization verification
- Load time testing

ACCESSIBILITY TESTS
-------------------
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Screen reader testing
- Keyboard navigation testing
- Color contrast verification

SECURITY TESTS
--------------
- Dependency vulnerability scanning
- Input validation testing
- XSS prevention verification
- CSRF protection testing

