PART 4: TECHNICAL DEBT & IMPROVEMENTS
================================================================================

CURRENT TECHNICAL DEBT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Missing Test Coverage (HIGH PRIORITY)
   - No tests written yet
   - Risk: Bugs in production
   - Impact: High

2. Incomplete Error Handling (HIGH PRIORITY)
   - API errors not properly surfaced
   - No error boundaries
   - Impact: Poor user experience on failures

3. Missing Loading States (MEDIUM PRIORITY)
   - Some components don't show loading
   - Impact: Confusing UX during data fetching

4. Accessibility Gaps (MEDIUM PRIORITY)
   - Missing ARIA labels
   - Keyboard navigation incomplete
   - Impact: Accessibility compliance issues

5. No Environment Variable Validation (LOW PRIORITY)
   - process.env used without validation
   - Impact: Runtime errors if misconfigured

RECOMMENDED IMPROVEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Add Error Boundary Component
   ```typescript
   // components/ErrorBoundary.tsx
   // Wrap app in error boundary for graceful error handling
   ```

2. Create API Client Utility
   ```typescript
   // lib/api/client.ts
   // Centralized API client with interceptors, error handling
   ```

3. Add Environment Variable Validation
   ```typescript
   // lib/env.ts
   // Validate required env vars at startup
   ```

4. Implement React Query or SWR
   - Better data fetching
   - Caching and revalidation
   - Loading/error states built-in

5. Add Storybook (Optional)
   - Component documentation
   - Visual testing
   - Design system showcase

