PART 5: BACKEND INTEGRATION GUIDE
================================================================================

CURRENT STATE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅ API layer structure ready (lib/api/stores.ts)
✅ Type definitions match expected responses
✅ Components accept data via props
✅ Environment variables configured
✅ Error handling structure in place (needs enhancement)

INTEGRATION STEPS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Update API Base URL
   ```bash
   # .env.local
   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.apsonic.com
   ```

2. Replace Static Data
   - lib/data/products.ts → API call
   - lib/data/stores.ts → API call (already has fetchStores)
   - lib/data/banners.ts → API call
   - lib/data/faq.ts → API call

3. Update Components
   - Convert Server Components to fetch data
   - Add loading states
   - Add error handling
   - Use React Query for client-side data

4. API Endpoints Expected
   ```
   GET /api/stores
   GET /api/stores?type=dealer&country=ghana
   GET /api/stores/:id
   GET /api/products
   GET /api/products/:id
   GET /api/banners
   GET /api/faq
   ```

5. Response Format
   - Should match TypeScript interfaces in lib/types/
   - JSON format
   - Proper HTTP status codes

